        "content": "## Compliance Scorecard by STIG + Benchmark Currency\nPer-STIG compliance for the selected **Collection**, joined to the STIG **library** so you can spot **outdated benchmark revisions**: compare *Rev in use* against *Latest rev*. `Pinned = true` means the collection is frozen on an old revision on purpose (or by neglect).\n\n*Two live queries joined on benchmarkId.*"
